items.what: Frankly, I'm glad no one showed up.
This ship is too tiny. It dodges taxes too easily.
Wonder if armor can be used as a tax write-off...
Not my fault the shopkeep didn't pay their taxes last year.
What kind of ship doesn't have a cockpit?!
We can hit that cockpit! I think!
Money, probably.
I don't think they're very safe...
Is this energy refund like a tax refund?
This ship makes no sense, it confuses me.
Blue all the way!
I got a bad feeling about this loop...
Everything is fine! The nanofibers SHOULD handle this one.
I don't think the nanofibers can handle that much!
We meant to miss! I think!
Wait, where did warp prep go? You can't do taxes without preparation!
Does being on this ship mean I'm the captain's parrot?
It means you're a dweeb.
Squawk! Tera wants a cracker!
How about a knuckle sandwich?
This cockpit change seems cowardly.
Fight smarter, not harder.
Personally, I think it is VERY valid to be cowardly.
Those missles better not come with sales tax.
I am SO glad we have armor right now.
I think we can file armor as a tax write-off!
Books?
W-wait, how do we operate a ship without a computer?
Did- Did someone just read my mind?
I don't want people in my head!
Energy readings are back to normal.
Wait, I thought crabs were like, government drones?
Are you sure these facts aren't government cover-ups?
I'm watching you, government crab drone.
If it helps the team... then... okay.
Wait wait, I was having a good dream!
D-Dizzy?
So long, space pirate!
I don't wanna die!
Yeah, me neither.
Is this where we reset?
Probably.
Are we gonna explode?!
Tera, breathe.
Please don't tell me we reset here...
Alright, I won't.
I don't wanna die!
You get used to it.
If I die, Drake's going down with me!
We're ALL going down, bird brain.
Hurry, hack their ship before we go kaboom!
That's illegal.
We're gonna explode!
No! We can do it!
About time to loop again.
B-but I don't wanna loop yet!
This run is scuffed.
Maybe it wouldn't be if you paid your taxes.
Welp.
Darn.
Tera! Tax us outta here!
I... What?
It's over man.
Yeah, I can feel it.
It's time to reset.
CAT? Don't scare me like this!
Wait, what do we do now?
Let's try not to hit the armor next time.
Yeah yeah! Hit that brittle point!
Chocolate-free cookies!
Don't we pay taxes to like, have people get RID of trash?
Woa, we're doing it!
Heck yeah!
We got this!
Bird up!
Nice one!
Nicer than you.
Too easy.
Would be easier if you paid your darn bills.
Can't believe we're trusting someone who's more of a wimp than I am.
I-I can't tax a missile.
Just shoot it down!
B-but I wanted that...
If we keep fighting, I might get airsickness...
Tera, take a break.
I'll get the puke bag!
Do birds get sick from flying?
But... you're a bird?
Birds... hate... flying...
I don't think I can handle another reset.
We might explode!
I can't believe you pulled that off.
Alright alright. Maybe space pirates DO have some skill.
Drake!
Drake, I swear to-
What are you gonna do, tax me to death?
This heat is gonna turn me into roast bird.
Woa, good job Peri!
No problem.
Peri!
Oh. Oh god.
Listen, we don't want the rocks, they're not good tax write-offs.
That is SO much wasted money, ya know.
Are you kidding me?
It sounds dangerous. Makes me a bit queasy.
PLEASE do not put your missiles as a tax write-off this year.
This guy definitely does not pay his taxes.
Can I have a few more minutes? I'm not ready yet!
Woah! We're killing it out here!
I don't think the ship is supposed to sound like that!
Uh... are we gonna be okay?
*disgruntled bird noises*
...What?
Hey, wait! They're going left! Those cheaters!
They're dodging right! Don't let them dodge their taxes!
Thank goodness we blocked that.
We've been here so long, I think I'm getting used to airsickness.
That smells like... acid?
Woa! Big hit!
That'll show those tax evaders.
Okay, we can survive this one.
We're safe!
Drake, cool it. Now.
Darn.
Next time we'll hit them. I hope.
I don't think we were supposed to miss.
Gosh darn it.
Woa, firing cannons isn't as hard as I thought.
We got this.
Good job.
Thank you!
Woa, I hit them!
At least you did SOMETHING right.
Heck yeah!
Woah, nice shot, me.
That's what you tax evaders get.
Nice one.
Thanks, Peri.
Woa, I did the big damage thing.
You did the thing!
Did you see that, Drake? That's how you get it done!
Whatever.
I didn't know I was this strong!
Tax time!
I'll get them to pay up, don't worry.
Time to start taxing.
Let's charge some cards.
Let's empty those bank accounts.
Carry the one...
Accrue that debt...
Just a little more tax...
C'mon, don't pay attention...
Holy tax time!
Pay your taxes next time!
Pay up, buttercup!
I love this job sometimes.
I... didn't mean to tax us this hard.
I can, uh, fix this.
Tera! Taxes!
Sorry, sorry!
I don't like paying my taxes.
I never knew they hurt this much.
I can't block all the taxes with shields!
I'll try to pay off the debt!
...You're scaring me.
Are taxes supposed to hurt?
I don't mean for them to!
I don't think taxes are supposed to work like this.
I don't know how to turn them off...
Taxes suck.
Sorry!
Tera. Why.
Oops!
Egg time!
Tera, where did you find that egg?
I dunno.
Was that an... egg?
Maybe.
It smells like egg in here.
It does?
...You did not.
I did.
Where did the egg come from?
I dunno.
Woa. Egg.
Egg indeed.
I want eggs for breakfast!
Books! No!
I don't think male birds can lay-
Shut it, CAT.
Take that, egghead!
We can't keep shooting eggs out of our cannons.
It's a valid tactical maneuver!
How did you boil an egg when we have no oven?
It takes a few hours.
Are eggs supposed to hurt?
Only when you throw them really, really hard.
I wonder if I can load eggs into my drones.
If you need ammo, I know where to find some.
Tera, PLEASE stop hogging up our fridge.
But my eggs need a place to sleep!
Wonder if this is an easter egg?
No, it's just a bird egg.
I'm egg-static!
And you're egg-ceptional!
These eggs are getting out of control.
...I didn't do it.
The perfect egg throw...
This is the best egg I have ever seen...
Thank you, my eggy friend.
Thank you for the extra funds!
A little cash goes a long way.
Hopefully I can buy us out of a pinch.
Ah! A morning snack!
A small energy boost to perk you up in the morning!
I think this will help us worm our way out of anything!
You know as they say! The early bird...
...gets the worm.
...I dunno, I usually sleep in.
...Catches their prey, of course.
...Flies?
...How about two birds, one stone?
...Makes me breakfast!
...I don't like worms in my code.
Setting alarms for 5AM, got it.
Your taxes are way past due!
Your yearly payments are due!
These extra taxes should give us an edge in this battle.
Aw yeah. It's tax time.
Capitalism has never caused any problems whatsoever.
Let's take a break, capitalism has given me more work to do.
It's time to charge those credit cards!
Phew! Glad I had some spare cash.
When in doubt, bribery always works.
The money from my tax refund sure came in handy!
Hopefully losing that bailout won't financially cripple me.
See that, Drake? Money is better than serenity!
I don't think thast's a good moral lesson to teach me.
Woah! Money is magic!
Not... exactly?
You're welcome, Drake.
Whatever.
I don't need your handouts.
These bailouts are mainly so I don't die while I'm next to you.
The power of money strikes again!
And this is why I steal money.
Time for takeoff.
Extra evade should always help!
Glad I got flight training! I didn't know how to fly a ship before.
Where did you get your pilot's license?
Oh, so you're a flightless bird? Noted.
So which flightless bird species are you?
...How are you even alive.
It's okay! I can teach you!
I forged my pilot's license!
Engaging autopilot mode.
Don't worry, CAT can steer on her own.
You've been pardoned.
A little kindness goes a long way.
You are officially forgiven for your tax sins.
I don't know what else to do. Let's just end this quickly.
I hope this play was the right one.
Desperate times call for desperate measures.
I think I can get us outta this mess!
I'm breaking us outta this fight.
I'm tapping into some funds. Let's hope it helps.
Just let me think here...
My bird brain will come up with something, just gimme a sec.
I think I got some extra ideas.
They're not escaping these taxes!
I was told to never give up. Let's hope that works now.
These taxes will never end.
Uhh, you're an egg smeller! Wait, that's not a good insult.
You remind me of buttered toast!
You remind me of Drake if they were cool!
You seriously need insult lessons.
You're like Dizzy if they didn't explode stuff!
What can I say, I'm good at what I do.
Uh... I can't insult someone so cute.
Insult the bad guy, not me!
You're just like Peri when she doesn't let me eat chicken nuggets!
We both know that's not a good idea.
Isaac and you would get along, you both like nerd stuff!
Thank... you?
You and Max would both like to watch cute cat videos online!
That would be fantastic.
You're just as grumpy as CAT!
I'm changing all of your passwords now.
You remind me of Riggs' boba addiction!
What addiction?
You taste like onions!
You have a tiny brain!
You don't pay your taxes on time!
I bet your taxes look like poopy!
Tera! Language!
Hey, watch what you're saying!
You look like a furry! ...Wait a minute.
I bet you failed flight school!
I bet you like science stuff!
Was that directed at me?
You should try being a bird next time! They're awesomer!
You're worse than a space pirate!
And you're worse than a tax collector.
You're... uh... aw beans, I can't think of anything.
I bet you wish you were taller!
You, um, look like a bird??? Listen, insults are hard.
You look like grumpy grass on a wind farm!
...What?
Yeah, that makes sense.
Huh?
I don't understand-
Is this a secret code?
I bet you don't even touch grass.
Wow! Grass!
Please speak coherently.
You smell like a bad hair day!
You probably were hatched from an egg!
I bet you're a gamer! Boo!
I bet your tax return was very small!
Your mom is probably very lovely!
You, erm... aren't good at video games?
Your ship reminds me of mobile game ads. Ew.
Hey, you... wait, no... ugh, nevermind.
I'm gonna tax you so hard, you're gonna have a negative bank account!
Stinky!
Stupid!
Speak for yourself.
Dummy!
I'm gonna kick your heiney!
Tera! Language!
Hey, watch what you're saying!
Your nose looks funny!
Speak for yourself.
Your ship sucks at literally everything!
I'm out of ideas. Can you just, insult yourself this time?
Consider your butt about to be kicked!
Tera! Language!
Hey, watch what you're saying!
I wish I could avoid you as much as people avoid taxes.
I bet you breathe too much!
Hmm... this paper says that you're a butthead.
Ugh. I don't even think you even deserve an insult.
I kinda don't wanna be mean right now. Just, look in the mirror or something.
I bet you play with motion controls. Gross.
Hmm... Have you tried makeup? It should help you out a bit.
Pack up your stuff and leave, you already lost!
I bet you use Bing! Ew!
I bet you don't like mustard!
Your head is shaped like an egg.
You look like moldy bread!
Uh... Your mom???
Tera, get back here!
Tera, please stop hiding.
Ah, the bird's hiding under the control panel again.
Ah! Tera knocked over my boba!
Never seen a bird waddle that fast.
Why doesn't he like, fly away?
Aww, he did the head bob thing as he ran away.
Tera, can you stop hiding underneath my drones?
He left his pilot seat again. Coward.
Chickening out, huh?
Tera, stop running my by monitors!
Huh. Didn't know birds can run that fast.
Tera! You knocked over my crystals!
While you're gone, can you pick me up some snacks?
Tera. To the cockpit. Now.
Sometimes, I wonder why we brought him on this ship.
